ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, because the course provided an overview of the question of empire through the perspectives of important thinkers in the European tradition.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Allowed me to understand the complex question of empire - especially its role and function in among European thinkers.

Helped to improve my understanding of the general course of European political thought and the place of empire therein; this is very helpful background to my own work, which focuses more narrowly on the 20th century.
